SkillGapAI is an advanced AI-driven career intelligence platform that bridges the gap between a candidate's current qualifications and the requirements of their target job roles by analyzing resumes and job descriptions to provide actionable insights. Developed through a structured milestone approach, the system utilizes a Flask-based backend to parse PDF resumes with PyMuPDF and perform semantic matching using BERT and spaCy NLP models to calculate a precise "Match Score". The platform's modern user interface is built with a high-tech "purple glass" aesthetic, featuring backdrop-blur effects and interactive data visualizations like Chart.js doughnut, radar, and stacked bar graphs that highlight matched versus missing skills. By identifying specific areas for improvement, SkillGapAI empowers job seekers to align their profiles with industry demands, all while running on a robust technical stack deployed via Vercel for professional-grade performance.
